data.description: Come see this beautiful home located in the Carlisle subdivision! This 3 bedroom 2 full bath home has been newly remodeled. It features a lovely fenced backyard, huge covered front porch, back patio for entertaining, and a cozy wood burning fireplace. This home has been well maintained throughout. All appliances are to remain. New roof installed 2023. The home warranty is transferable and valid though March 2024. Call your favorite Realtor for a private showing.
